|---|---|---|
| `Result<T,E>` (`ok: true/false`) + `Ok`/`Err`/`mapResult`/`andThen`/`collect` | `core/ai-sdk/src/core/server/result.ts` | Custom (hand-rolled) |
| `neverthrow` `Result<T,E>` with `.match()` | `packages/app-config/src/parse.ts` | `neverthrow@8.2.0` (catalog, single consumer) |
| `{ ok: true } \| { ok: false }` inline | `api/platform/src/lib/oauth/authorize.ts` | None |
